data.description: Great mountain views to the west. Set up for horses with shelters, corrals and  arena, fully fenced.  Front and rear landscaping. Updated kitchen and bathrooms, roof cover, vinyl siding, on demand hot water heater, furnace.  Needs carpet and paint pick your own colors.  Fireplace in living room, central air conditioning.  Fully fenced, RV gates and parking.  Sold "AS IS" Subject to Court Approval and possibly the Over-Bid Process. Subject to NRS148.120.
